  "body": "### Description\n\nI think that dev mode can out-of-the-box support changing the test port in dev mode to allow continuous testing when user bounds the application HTTP port to 8081 with `quarkus.http.port=8081`.\r\n\r\nCurrent behavior:\r\n\r\n`Caused by: io.quarkus.runtime.QuarkusBindException: Port(s) already bound: 8081: Address already in use`\r\n\r\n\n\n### Implementation ideas\n\nJust change to any free port to simulate the behavior as if the user would add the configuration `quarkus.http.test-port=0` for instance or any different free port. ",
